ActTerritorial Lands Act
PrecisORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (AKAITCHO DENE FIRST NATIONS, N.W.T.) - which provides withdrawal from disposal the surface and subsurface rights of certain lands (approximately 62,000 square kilometres), in order to facilitate the settlement of the Akaitcho Dene First Nations Final Agreement in the Northwest Territories.
